      "message": "the existing ncmp controller code does not use 'dataType'. If we are planning to keep it the same in the Instanbul release, then we should mention it somewhere. \n\nPlease have a look at line 92 of the DmiRestController.java\n\nhttps://gerrit.onap.org/r/gitweb?p=cps/ncmp-dmi-plugin.git;a=blob;f=src/main/java/org/onap/cps/ncmp/dmi/rest/controller/DmiRestController.java;h=37381fb1fab57129951a92f8353963441d0fd146;hb=refs/heads/master\n\n\n@Override\n  87     public ResponseEntity<String> writeDataByPassthroughRunningForCmHandle(\n  88         final DataAccessWriteRequest dataAccessWriteRequest,\n  89         final String cmHandle, final String resourceIdentifier) {\n  90         final String response = dmiService.writeResourceDataPassthroughForCmHandle(cmHandle,\n  91             resourceIdentifier,\n  92             MediaType.APPLICATION_JSON_VALUE,\n  93             dataAccessWriteRequest.getData());\n  94         return new ResponseEntity<>(response, HttpStatus.CREATED);\n  95     }\n  96",
